column4: NSLOCTEXT("[01BBB4EE40E303336D1B40852305A274]", "67E4957543D634DAFCFCCA9033829982", "Hey, do you want to play a match with me? If you win, I\'ll do whatever you say.")
NSLOCTEXT("[01BBB4EE40E303336D1B40852305A274]", "1A0FF09749E5ABEFBC4CDA99D1B98472", "What I call... Digimon Curling! I\'ll tell you more inside.")
NSLOCTEXT("[01BBB4EE40E303336D1B40852305A274]", "8AA2EB28492B4B6561FABA88D902C7C1", "Nothing the first time. But next time you have to give me a fish first.")
NSLOCTEXT("[01BBB4EE40E303336D1B40852305A274]", "9316F6F7411455C82F9D1BAC9BABE250", "Then if I win, you come to the city with me. OK?")
NSLOCTEXT("[01BBB4EE40E303336D1B40852305A274]", "4076D81F466E32E01E8A2FB27E237216", "Amazing dude. I lost a match for the first time.")
NSLOCTEXT("[01BBB4EE40E303336D1B40852305A274]", "036F68174BA33162916C9980E9B736BD", "Alright, now come to the city with me as you promised.")
NSLOCTEXT("[01BBB4EE40E303336D1B40852305A274]", "9C797D4048043C39AE347781BD7714AF", "Oh well, I guess I have to. But I already decided what I\'m going to do in the city.")
NSLOCTEXT("[01BBB4EE40E303336D1B40852305A274]", "13A7A6EF4B0AED3F99B0B283DDEE9FD7", "Sorry bro. Come back again to challenge me. And don\'t forget to bring another fish.")
NSLOCTEXT("[01BBB4EE40E303336D1B40852305A274]", "90F1310E464B03DC32D4E5AA5302D51F", "Impressive! Perfect score! Are you by any chance... a professional?")
